Add metrics from Cilium 1.17-1.19 not covered by PR 22765: endpoint propagation delay, datapath signals/conntrack GC interval, BPF maps/progs counts, policy selector cache, ACT connection tracking, BGP control plane, drift checker, XDS events, operator workqueue/hive jobs/identity GC latency/endpoint GC/BGP/LBIPAM, plus disabled-by-default metrics (statedb, reconciler, neighbor, NAT GC, FQDN semaphore, hive degraded) and all feature metrics.